---
title: Peppercorn Pork Chops with Rosemary Mashed Potatoes and Roasted Broccoli
description: There’s nothing more comforting than mashed potatoes and gravy. It’s up there with fried chicken, meatloaf, and your grandmother’s apple pie. We’re making a non-traditional gravy with a bit of shallot, rosemary, and black peppercorns for flavor. You’ll want to drizzle it over everything!
